de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.OpenInfraOrderBy

  • Packages that use OpenInfraOrderBy 
    Package Description
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.daos
    This package implements all DAO classes which are used to access the JPA persistence layer (database).
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.rbac
    This package contains classes of the role-based access control system (RBAC).
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest
    This package provides classes used to produce the JSON and XML outputs for RESTful services related to both projects and system database schemas.
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.meta
    Domain classes used to produce the JSON and XML output for the RESTful services related to the meta database schema.
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.project
    This package contains REST resources which exclusively refer to the project databases.
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.rbac
    This package contains REST interfaces for role-based access control (rbac).
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.system
    This package contains REST resources which exclusively refer to the system database.
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.view
    This package contains the view components in order to provide a graphical user interface.
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.view.project
